FBIS4-2188 "drchi067_o_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-067 Daily Report 6 Apr 1994 REGIONAL AFFAIRS East Region Shandong Begins Digital Communications Network Shandong Begins Digital Communications Network SK0704024794 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 6 Apr 94 SK0704024794 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Excerpt] The digital communications network which provides various modernized communications means has recently been completed and made available in the province. This is an indication that the comprehensive communications capacity of the province's postal and telecommunications departments has joined the world's high ranks. The digital communications network is a new communications method combining computers with modern communications technology. The digital communications network now available in the province is a network with diverse functions and group exchanges and is of a high world level. With this equipment, the province is able to conduct digital communications with all cities at or above the city and prefectural levels in the province, with 30 capital cities, most cities at or above the city and prefectural levels, and some cities at the county level in the country, and with 23 countries and regions in the world, including the United States, Japan, France, and Germany. [passage omitted]
